title.narrative: DRR AND EMERGENCY CAPACITY STRENGTHENED

description.narrative: National and local capacities for risk-informed and child-centred DRR are strengthened., which contributes to Disaster Risk Reduction, Environmental Sustainability, Other Cross-Sectoral Programme Areas, Prevention And Response Services For Violence Against Children. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Developing And Leveraging Resources And Partnerships, Evaluations, Research And Data, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By end of CP improved capacity of public sector institutions at the national and local level to prepare for and mitigate risks from emergencies/hazards in line with UNICEF Core Commitments for Children.
